Calculations were performed by the Gaussian 16 revision E01 series of programs using one hybrid density functional M06-2X
and the SMD implicit solvation model. Geometries were fully optimized in aqueous solution. Harmonic frequencies were calculated to confirm that
the structures were minima on the potential energy surface and to obtain the thermal and entropic contributions to the free energies.
